ZH: 请你留心宝贵的时间。
EN: Please be mindful of your valuable time.

ZH: 小心留意路上的危险。
EN: Be careful and watch out for dangers on the road.

ZH: 火车驶过时，请留心站台边缘。
EN: Please be mindful of the platform edge when the train passes.

ZH: 在外面旅行时，要留心盗窃。
EN: When traveling outside, be mindful of theft.

ZH: 坐车时，别忘了留心站点的变动。
EN: When taking a bus, don't forget to stay aware of any changes in stops.

ZH: 留心感受到他人的情绪变化。
EN: Pay attention to the changes in others' emotions.

ZH: 情绪起伏时，必须留心自己的行为。
EN: When experiencing emotional ups and downs, it is important to be mindful of one's own actions.

ZH: 外出购物时，留心价格的波动。
EN: Be mindful of price fluctuations when going shopping.

ZH: 他给了我一个留心的眼神，表示要我小心。
EN: He gave me a mindful look, indicating that I should be careful.

ZH: 在人群中留心保持安全距离。
EN: Be mindful and maintain a safe distance in crowds.

